---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Ventures"
  description="Sandra Weise's ventures — Finnish Bistro, A Better Question podcast, The Happy Class, Resonance Den, and life coaching and speaking."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="page-hero page-hero--image" style="background-image: url('/images/ventures-hero.png');">
    <div class="page-hero__overlay" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="container page-hero__inner">
      <p class="section-label">Ventures</p>
      <h1>Five businesses.<br />One <span class="accent">mission</span>.</h1>
      <p class="page-hero__desc">Every venture exists to serve the same purpose — authentic connection, transformation, and raising the vibration of the world around me.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Finnish Bistro -->
  <section class="section bg-cream" id="finnish-bistro">
    <div class="container venture-detail">
      <div class="venture-detail__badge venture-detail__badge--emerald">
        <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 8h1a4 4 0 0 1 0 8h-1"/><path d="M2 8h16v9a4 4 0 0 1-4 4H6a4 4 0 0 1-4-4V8z"/><line x1="6" y1="1" x2="6" y2="4"/><line x1="10" y1="1" x2="10" y2="4"/><line x1="14" y1="1" x2="14" y2="4"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="venture-detail__content">
        <img src="/images/venture-bistro.png" alt="" class="venture-detail__img" aria-hidden="true" />
        <h2>Finnish Bistro</h2>
        <p class="venture-detail__role">Where it all started — community institution</p>
        <p>A St. Paul staple. Finnish Bistro has been serving the community for years — great food, great people, and the kind of atmosphere that makes you want to stay longer than you planned. It's where neighbors become friends and where Sandra's philosophy of human-first business lives in every detail.</p>
        <p>Sandra leads with connection. She knows every person on her team by name and makes time for each of them — not to talk about work, but to talk about life. That's not a management technique. That's how Sandra runs everything.</p>
        <a href="https://finnishbistro.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn--secondary btn--small">Visit Finnish Bistro &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <!-- A Better Question -->
  <section class="section bg-cream" id="a-better-question">
    <div class="container venture-detail">
      <div class="venture-detail__badge venture-detail__badge--indigo">
        <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 1a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v8a3 3 0 0 0 6 0V4a3 3 0 0 0-3-3z"/><path d="M19 10v2a7 7 0 0 1-14 0v-2"/><line x1="12" y1="19" x2="12" y2="23"/><line x1="8" y1="23" x2="16" y2="23"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="venture-detail__content">
        <img src="/images/venture-podcast.png" alt="" class="venture-detail__img" aria-hidden="true" />
        <h2>A Better Question</h2>
        <p class="venture-detail__role">The attention engine — podcast &middot; content platform</p>
        <p>The podcast about the questions we avoid, the conversations we need, and the relationships that define our lives. After twenty years of coaching, Sandra is taking the questions that have transformed thousands of lives and putting them on the air.</p>
        <p>Every episode is designed to do one thing: make you stop and think. About your relationship. About what you're avoiding. About what would change if you just asked a better question.</p>
        <a href="/podcast" class="btn btn--secondary btn--small">Browse Episodes &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <!-- The Happy Class -->
  <section class="section bg-cream" id="the-happy-class">
    <div class="container venture-detail">
      <div class="venture-detail__badge venture-detail__badge--rose">
        <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="venture-detail__content">
        <img src="/images/venture-happy-class.png" alt="" class="venture-detail__img" aria-hidden="true" />
        <h2>The Happy Class</h2>
        <p class="venture-detail__role">The life's work — product &middot; passion &middot; purpose</p>
        <p>A DIY alternative to couples counseling. Not for broken relationships — for couples who are good but want to be great. The Happy Class is a physical product that couples do together, built on twenty years of Sandra's coaching expertise.</p>
        <p><em>"Making something good even better."</em> That's the tagline, and it's the philosophy behind everything. Most couples don't need therapy. They need better structure, better questions, and a safe way to do the work together.</p>
        <p>Launching October 2026. The couples kit is first — then friends, siblings, mothers and daughters, fathers and sons.</p>
        <a href="#" class="btn btn--accent btn--small">Join the Waitlist &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <!-- Resonance Den -->
  <section class="section bg-cream" id="resonance-den">
    <div class="container venture-detail">
      <div class="venture-detail__badge venture-detail__badge--amethyst">
        <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="venture-detail__content">
        <img src="/images/venture-resonance.png" alt="" class="venture-detail__img" aria-hidden="true" />
        <h2>Resonance Den</h2>
        <p class="venture-detail__role">The sacred space — crystals &middot; meditation &middot; community</p>
        <p>A curated collection of crystals, gemstones, and sacred space in St. Paul. Resonance Den is part retail, part community hub. The meditation room is offered free to the community — prayer groups, 12-step meetings, meditation circles. Everyone is welcome.</p>
        <p>Sandra hand-selected the entire crystal collection. Every piece is intentional. This space is a physical expression of everything she believes about energy, intention, and creating room for people to do their inner work.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <!-- Coaching & Speaking -->
  <section class="section bg-cream" id="coaching-speaking">
    <div class="container venture-detail">
      <div class="venture-detail__badge venture-detail__badge--citrine">
        <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="venture-detail__content">
        <img src="/images/venture-coaching.jpg" alt="" class="venture-detail__img" aria-hidden="true" />
        <h2>Coaching & Speaking</h2>
        <p class="venture-detail__role">The original practice — 20+ years &middot; transformation &middot; truth</p>
        <p>Trained under Iyanla Vanzant on the Oprah Winfrey Network. Over two decades of sitting across from people in the moments that matter most — when they realize the life they built isn't the life they want, and they decide to do something about it.</p>
        <p>Sandra speaks on purpose-driven leadership, authentic relationship building, resilience, and transformation. She doesn't do motivational fluff. She asks the hard questions and helps people find their own answers.</p>
        <a href="/work-with-me" class="btn btn--secondary btn--small">Book Sandra &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    padding: calc(72px + var(--space-xl)) 0 var(--space-xl);
    position: relative;
  }

  .page-hero--image {
    background-color: var(--espresso);
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .page-hero__overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(120deg, rgba(44, 29, 18, 0.82) 0%, rgba(44, 29, 18, 0.55) 100%);
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .page-hero__inner {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .page-hero h1 {
    color: var(--linen);
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  .page-hero__desc {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: rgba(250, 246, 240, 0.6);
    max-width: 560px;
  }

  .accent { color: var(--citrine); }

  /* Venture image */
  .venture-detail__img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 520px;
    max-height: 60vh;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 1.25rem;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgba(44, 29, 18, 0.1);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .venture-detail__img {
      height: 360px;
    }
  }

  /* Venture Detail */
  .venture-detail {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .venture-detail__badge {
    width: 72px;
    height: 72px;
    border-radius: 1.25rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    position: sticky;
    top: calc(72px + 2rem);
  }

  .venture-detail__badge--emerald { background: rgba(61, 153, 112, 0.1); color: var(--emerald); }
  .venture-detail__badge--indigo { background: rgba(61, 79, 143, 0.1); color: var(--indigo); }
  .venture-detail__badge--rose { background: rgba(232, 180, 184, 0.15); color: var(--ruby); }
  .venture-detail__badge--amethyst { background: rgba(139, 109, 176, 0.1); color: var(--amethyst); }
  .venture-detail__badge--citrine { background: rgba(212, 168, 67, 0.12); color: var(--citrine); }

  .venture-detail__content h2 {
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .venture-detail__role {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .venture-detail__content p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .venture-detail__content em {
    color: var(--text-dark);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .venture-detail__content .btn {
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .venture-detail__stats {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .stat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .stat__number {
    font-family: 'Lora', serif;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--espresso);
  }

  .stat__label {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-top: 0.125rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .venture-detail {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .venture-detail__badge {
      position: static;
    }
  }
</style>
